Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.21,0:00:06.83,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Kanie's tutoring,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:09.96,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm done studying for my test.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:12.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, that's alright.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.73,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've got plenty of time, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}N-No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:20.22,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He meant plenty of time to {\i0}study{\i1}... right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:25.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,The 25 Year Old High School Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:25.88,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(55.333,697.667)}Episode 8: On That Day, At That Time, In That Place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.43,0:00:27.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,He fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:35.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,If he was that tired, he shouldn't have stayed up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.08,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's backwards from when we were in school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:43.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What could he have meant by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, Kanie had longer hair...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:49.18,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...he even dyed it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:52.46,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He was even less approachable than he is now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.65,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:00:56.30,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:58.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to wake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.67,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:03.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,And these cloths... I promise I'll wash and return them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.71,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Are you {\i1}trying{\i0} to turn me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:12.89,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:15.84,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,K-Kanie, are you sure not still half asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.16,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.57,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Stop! Y-You said we wouldn't do this kind of thing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.57,0:01:22.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I never promised anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.33,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,T-That's playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:27.58,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You always mislead me when it comes to the most important details.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.01,0:01:29.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:32.23,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What do you want me to say to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:34.74,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What? He's asking {\i0}me{\i1}?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:37.68,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do {\i0}I{\i1} want {\i0}him{\i1} to say?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Too bad, your time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.21,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no use.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.21,0:02:01.00,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't think clearly anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What, embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:10.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:12.93,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,K-Kanie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:19.05,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're already soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:20.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Does it feel that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.45,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.33,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:27.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Look at me, Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I can feel how hot you are inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:37.76,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.94,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-No, Kanie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.28,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,A-Any more and I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.14,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That night, I had a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:03.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.03,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Natori. Did you forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.75,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.98,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Being forced to do makeup lessons until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.19,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Apparently I have a make-up text next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.02,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,S-Sounds rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:19.76,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Not like this crap will do me any good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:23.91,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,B-But you never know what \Nmight be useful in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:27.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will come in useful, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:30.43,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Do you find people like me hard to deal with?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:32.35,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.07,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Useful in the future, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:36.73,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Do you have any plans for your future?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:41.09,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Well, I used to, but I think it's a little late for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.49,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,It's never too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:47.01,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,I think just having a dream is really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:51.10,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Especially since I haven't been able to find one for myself, even after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.50,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Sorry, we weren't talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:58.59,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Then what do you say to helping me study?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:03.25,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,What? B-But I'm really not all that smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:04.51,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,You're smarter than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:09.38,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Umm, so what is it you want to be in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.51,0:04:11.40,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,Not telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.75,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.44,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I completely forgot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:21.32,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be that Kanie had feelings for me back then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.06,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.62,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:27.86,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll ask.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:30.95,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you want me to say to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.80,Dialoge,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was really underhanded of him to put me on the spot like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:49.21,Songs,,0,0,0,,Who could have predicted this reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:57.01,Songs,,0,0,0,,I reel in this thread of memory, and use it to spin my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:05:01.89,Songs,,0,0,0,,Why are you all pushy one minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:07.65,Songs,,0,0,0,,and then gentle the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:13.15,Songs,,0,0,0,,As long as the two of us share this secret
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.15,0:05:18.71,Songs,,0,0,0,,it will be the light that guides you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:23.49,Songs,,0,0,0,,to somewhere in the yet-unknowable future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:27.93,Songs,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it's okay to optimistic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:31.97,Songs,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:37.41,Songs,,0,0,0,,hidden deep within those eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.41,0:05:42.67,Songs,,0,0,0,,I can't control these feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:49.83,Songs,,0,0,0,,Piece by piece, my heart is being snatched away
